Day 80: Jenkins Chained Builds

Date: December 16, 2025
Overview
Connected multiple jobs in a workflow.
Key Concepts Learned

Upstream/downstream relationships
Build triggers
Parameter passing between jobs
Pipeline orchestration

Configuration
groovypost {
    success {
        build job: 'integration-tests', 
              parameters: [string(name: 'BUILD_NUMBER', value: "${BUILD_NUMBER}")]
    }
}

Challenges Faced
Managing dependencies and ensuring proper execution order.
